        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Connecting the Community To End Military Suicide Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires each military department to authorize its respective service members to take up to two weeks of permissive temporary duty each year to attend a seminar, retreat, workshop, or outdoor recreational therapy event hosted by a nonprofit organization that focuses on psychological, physical, spiritual, or social wellness.<br> </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
